e not going to give up eating meat. Only 5% of Americans identify as vegeta=
rian, and 3% as vegan [https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJwlUUuSpSAQPM1jp8H=
PfrhgMZu5hlFCqUwrGIBtePsp-kVA5iLJqiLLQcU15ceeqVTWYKrPiTbiXXasFTO7CuYpeCsNV1=
Jp5q32wgyGhTItGfGAsNuaL2TnNe_BQQ0pNoMalB7YZgEkh2Ue3fhGI0bwSqEe5kUILjya96ctX=
