le farming, especially, gives rise to enormous amounts of greenhouse gases,=
 much of which is due to forests being cleared for grazing (so much for you=
r vision of happy cows living out truncated lives in relative freedom!).=20
Thus, there are both moral and practical reasons to abolish the practice of=
