jkn2NFnrEomZfsqIaFMfwGvoagi] =E2=80=94 enough to be competitive with fossil=
 fuels.=20
Now there=E2=80=99s no ironclad guarantee that a similar feat will be possi=
ble with tissue-culture meat. Not every conceivable thing can be invented a=
nd produced at low cost. But the encouraging recent progress in the field m=
erits a lot of investment. Some of this will be provided by venture capital=
 =E2=80=94 funding for tissue-culture meat startups is skyrocketing [https:=
//email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJwlkc2u4yAMhZ-m7BLxl5YsWMxmXiMy4CbMJCYC0ihvf8mt=
hHwM1rHRZw8V55Qvu6dS2R2meu1oCc-yYq2Y2VEwTzFYabiSSrNgdRBmMCyW6Z0RN4irrflAth9=
